rfcd_comment: Because the ready_for_certification_date was incorrectly recorded for ~2 years
when there were multiple values for this flag in the transition_name column
we must skip ~12K reports where the v1.2 API returns the correct (last) value
and the v1.1 API returns the incorrect (first) value.

select report_id, cert_count.sum from (select report_id, (select sum(case hmm when 'ready_for_certification' then 1 else 0 end) from unnest(transition_name) as hmm) from audit_singleauditchecklist where submission_status = 'disseminated') as cert_count where cert_count.sum > 1
